      "description": "Get ready to own a true masterpiece! This stunning vehicle is in absolute mint condition, looking and driving exactly like it did the day it left the showroom. Every inch has been meticulously cared for, from the flawless paint to the pristine interior, making it a perfect find for any serious collector or enthusiast.",
