      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care rarely seen in the pre-owned market. This is a singular opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a machine that remains in showroom state, offering an uncompromising driving experience and peerless aesthetic appeal.",
