    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it still drives like a total dream. It's spotless inside and out, with no scratches or dings to be found anywhere. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the massive dealership price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
