    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car has been preserved in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining its deep factory brilliance with no swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, further protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the hand-stitched leather remains supple with zero bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a voluminous binder of service records documenting every oil change and preventative maintenance task performed exclusively by master technicians. From the spotless engine bay to the untouched undercarriage, this is a rare opportunity to own a specimen that is indistinguishable from new. Inspections by specialists are welcomed and encouraged to verify the unparalleled state of this vehicle.",
      "price": 48500.0,
